A Powerful collection of programs Coded in Visual Basic (VB.NET) Language

((by me))

These programs are:

1. M-Write; A Simple word processor
2. M-Browse; A Powerful web browser
3. M-Time; A Basic calendar
4. M-Usic; An Ultimate Media Player (Plays: Images, Music, & Movies)
5. M-Calc; A Useful Scientific Calculator



*Addendum For M-Suite:

The Newest Version of M-Suite (2.0.0.0) Has MUCH Better GUI(graphical user interface)'s, such as icons, splash screens.

Better coded & Easier to use.
